quests/58\">\n              <span class=\"badge-category-bg\" style=\"background-color:#9CD326\"></span>\n              <span class=\"badge-category clear-badge\"><span class=\"category-name\">Feature Requests - API and Apps Framework</span></span>\n            </a>\n          </span>\n          <span class=\"subcategory\">\n            <a class=\"badge-wrapper bullet\" href=\"/c/developers/mondayapps/57\">\n              <span class=\"badge-category-bg\" style=\"background-color:#0088CC\"></span>\n              <span class=\"badge-category clear-badge\"><span class=\"category-name\">FAQs - Building monday Apps</span></span>\n            </a>\n          </span>\n          <span class=\"subcategory\">\n            <a class=\"badge-wrapper bullet\" href=\"/c/developers/share-monday-apps/61\">\n              <span class=\"badge-category-bg\" style=\"background-color:#66CCFF\"></span>\n              <span class=\"badge-category clear-badge\"><span class=\"category-name\">Share your monday apps!</span></span>\n            </a>\n          </span>\n          <span class=\"subcategory\">\n            <a class=\"badge-wrapper bullet\" href=\"/c/developers/api-faqs/59\">\n              <span class=\"badge-category-bg\" style=\"background-color:#00C875\"></span>\n              <span class=\"badge-category clear-badge\"><span class=\"category-name\">FAQs - GraphQL API</span></span>\n            </a>\n          </span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\n  </article>\n  <div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\n</aside>\n\n<p>Feel free to post this request there to see how we can best help. If you think this could be bug, email us at <a href=\"mailto:support@monday.com\">support@monday.com</a>.</p>"
